Dwarven Realms of Aetheria
The dwarves primarily inhabit the continent of Khazadnor, a rugged, mountain-dominated landmass roughly the size of North America. It lies northwest of Veloria across the Stormsea. The surface is harsh and inhospitable, so dwarven civilization is built almost entirely underground in vast networks of halls, mines, and fortresses.
Total dwarven population: ≈ 11.8 million (low due to long wars, low birth rates, and dangerous living conditions).
There are 8 Sovereign Great Holds, all independent but often forming temporary alliances. Several have major underground borders with demonic territories.

